title: Ubon Kruanapat F.C.
text: Ubon Kruanapat Football Club (<a href="Thai%20alphabet">Thai</a> สโมสรฟุตบอลอุบล ครัวนภัส), is a Thai professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Ubon%20Ratchathani%20Province">Ubon Ratchathani Province</a>. The club was formed in 2009 and entered the <a href="Thai%20League%203">Thai League 3</a> Northeastern region.
